title: Episode 01
description:
Welcome to Radio Rental. A mysterious video rental store with a tape collection of TRUE scary stories narrated by the people that experienced them.

On today’s tapes…

>> Chaos On A Flight
A young man feels the powerful adrenaline of fight or flight… while trapped on a plane.

 >> 404 Not Found
Another man believes in the randomness of the universe… maybe to a fault.
